              that metabolism plays in supporting the performance of individual
              synapses, including the relative contributions from postsynaptic
              responses, astrocytes, and presynaptic vesicle cycling. We
              propose a simple computational model for our excitatory cultures
              that accurately captures the inability of metabolically
              compromised synapses to sustain synchronous bursting when
              extracellular glucose is depleted.",
